-----------------------------------------------------------
    Overview
-----------------------------------------------------------
- mode to improve readability
- allow any number of spaces between tokens
	- \d is a single token
	- a character class is a single token
- for flavours supporting mode modifiers can put (?x) at start to start free-space mode

-----------------------------------------------------------
    Comments
-----------------------------------------------------------
- start comment with # until end of line
	- not supported by XPath and Oracle
- comments without free-space with (?#comment)